OL,3,CMan, 45, charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter Golders Green attack
OL,6,FEssa Suleiman, 45, has been charged
OL,7,Fwith attempted murder after two Jewish
OL,8,Fmen were stabbed in Golders Green,
OL,9,Fnorth London, on Wednesday.
OL,11,FHe was charged following a Counter
OL,12,FTerrorism Policing investigation into
OL,13,Fthe attack ` the latest in a series of
OL,14,Fattacks on Jewish sites over recent
OL,15,Fweeks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
