OL,3,CMan, 45, charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter Golders Green attack
OL,6,FFollowing authorisation from the Crown
OL,7,FProsecution Service, Essa Suleiman, of
OL,8,FCamberwell, south London, has been
OL,9,Fcharged with two counts of attempted
OL,10,Fmurder and one count of possession of
OL,11,Fa bladed article in a public place.
OL,13,FSuleiman was also charged with
OL,14,Fattempted murder in relation to a
OL,15,Fseparate incident on the same date in
OL,16,FGreat Dover Street.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
