OL,3,CMan, 45, charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter Golders Green attack
OL,6,FHe has been remanded in police custody
OL,7,Fand is due to appear at Westminster
OL,8,FMagistrates' Court on Friday, 1 May.
OL,10,FPolice tasered and arrested the
OL,11,Fsuspect after the double stabbing
OL,12,Fwhich saw two Jewish men ` Shloime
OL,13,FRand, 34, and Moshe Ben Baila, 76,
OL,14,Fnamed locally as Moshe Shine ` taken
OL,15,Fto hospital.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
