OL,3,CMan, 45, charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter Golders Green attack
OL,6,FMr Rand has been discharged from
OL,7,Fhospital and is now recovering at home
OL,8,Fafter receiving stitches, Rabbi Levi
OL,9,FSchapiro from the Jewish Community
OL,10,FCouncil, who has visited both victims,
OL,11,Fsaid on social media.
OL,13,FMr Shine remains in hospital and in a
OL,14,Fstable condition.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
