OL,3,CMan, 45, charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter Golders Green attack
OL,6,FCommander Helen Flanagan, Head of
OL,7,FCounter Terrorism Policing London,
OL,8,Fwhich is leading the investigation
OL,9,Fsaid: "Our thoughts remain with the
OL,10,Fvictims involved and specialist
OL,11,Fofficers continue to provide them with
OL,12,Fsupport as their recovery continues.
OL,14,F"We are determined to get justice for
OL,15,Fthe victims and now that a person has
OL,16,Fbeen charged, I would urge everyone to
OL,17,Favoid any further speculation in
OL,18,Frelation to this case so that justice
OL,19,Fcan run its course."
